  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Data protection for education providers
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Steps data protection officers and organisation heads of education providers should take to stay compliant with data protection laws when the UK leaves the EU.</p>

  </div>
</div>

